# Gateway build ignore. NOTE: this service builds from the REPO ROOT context
# (its go.mod replace reaches ../../packages/proto/gen/go), so Docker applies
# the context-root ignore rules, not this file. It is kept here to document the
# service's own excludable artifacts and to apply when the dir is built alone
# (e.g. `docker build services/gateway`). Image cleanliness does not depend on
# it: the Dockerfile COPYs only go.mod/go.sum, the package sources, and the
# proto module — never the items below.
gateway            # prebuilt local binary (services/gateway/gateway)
*.test
*_test.go
.git
.github
**/__pycache__
**/target
node_modules
*.log
.env
.env.*
